*.FullName

# Fork-specific
# SPEC.md is the internal engineering brief — not for the public repo.
SPEC.md
# Maintainer briefings for individual releases — same reason, kept local.
MAINTAINER_BRIEFING*.md
# patches/ holds the historical Python hot-patch — superseded by the TS fork.
patches/
# references/ holds frozen upstream snapshots for diffing — not part of fork source.
references/
# studio-plugin/out is the compiled Luau output (rbxtsc); rebuilt by `npm run build`.
studio-plugin/out/
# Compiled rbxmx artifacts — produced by `npm run build:plugin`, attached to GitHub releases.
studio-plugin/MCPPlugin.rbxmx
studio-plugin/MCPInspectorPlugin.rbxmx